{"tid":1670404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三毛黨叫大家去加泰集會 solomon叫大家唔好去 三毛黨就開始轉攻勢攻擊solomon","createTime":"2019-10-23T03:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T06:32:47.000Z","uid":48315,"like":46,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e4b7195d252cdd73e9f0cd5baf82634863ed28","tid":1670404,"uid":48315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"連陪突然多左勁多攻擊solomon既post<br />\n又攻擊佢人格<br />\n又問點解要信佢<br />\n又話佢係華人 係中共間諜<br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你地老母啦<br />\n人地係共和黨地位咁高 反共反到咁撚明顯<br />\n識中文 係bbc到話日日都用幾粒鐘睇香港新聞<br />\n對香港既認知一定多過哂所有美國議員<br />\n仲要係共和黨大佬 熟識美國政界<br />\n佢比既意見一定係對香港最有幫忙(係美國角度)<br />\n<br />\n至於加泰 我唔係想割<br />\n但一句講哂 依家連登因為加泰分化到咁<br />\n個傷害真係好大<br />\n我覺我真係爭議咁大 不如就多一事不如少一事<br />\n<br />\n最後咁講 我們沒有分化的本錢"},{"pid":"424c9b7481ed676f0b1ba8bfb503c681f6a7ba78","tid":1670404,"uid":48315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:41:23.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c0eb78fdb35489b52b56cbcf93a721906cf00c46","tid":1670404,"uid":48315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"fefb578e598c2328c25055d01e84cced6ae715b1","tid":1670404,"uid":44298,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"口交部同五毛都想我地集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f371576eb0a02573e3580a44c18374b6691f3c","tid":1670404,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/caCxF6x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcaCxF6x.jpg&h=c4418fdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8026e0b42608fb1eb3b3377e88f6a296a644ea6","tid":1670404,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"希望樓主俾like我呢個post：<br />\n<br />\n【瓦解分化妙計】建議連仔<span style=\"color: red;\">加設五毛、分化撚、mon post狗</span>等標籤識別功能，並以<span style=\"color: red;\">唔同顏色</span>顯示該等被標籤嘅用戶名俾自己睇（標籤